data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful split level home in the highly sought-after community of Saint Michael. Upon entering, you will be greeted by the real white oak hardwood flooring that flows throughout the main level. The open concept layout is perfect for entertaining, with a large deck off the informal dining room where you can enjoy outdoor meals and gatherings. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing plenty of space for everyone to spread out and relax. The newly painted walls, updated light fixtures, and new rod-iron banister create a fresh and modern feel. Outside, you will find a flat, large lot that backs up to a private wooded area, offering peace and tranquility. The 2 car attached garage provides convenient parking and storage space for your vehicles and belongings.

This home is a must-see for anyone looking for a comfortable and stylish living space in Saint Michael. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a showing today!
